TITLE: MOYURU - DISPLACEMENT TOP! 12-14
NOTES: Moyuru Collections are designed with the pursuit of free expression and unrivaled originality in mind, focusing on artistic forms inspired by "the Earth", "the Wind" and "Freedom". Japanese in influence and coloured by nature you are encouraged to wear your seasons together, layer with layer, in a statement of your own fashion personality. The fit is often oversized - designed to be worn loosely, allowing the garment's design features to do all the work. For sizing assistance use the myFit Tool or contact your favourite store, listed at the bottom of the page. The Displacement Top is a light, layering piece in flaring style. The top is made up of angular panels which finish at different lengths, creating a choppy, up and down hemline. Layer over a contrasting coloured pants, dresses or skirts to show off the hemline to best effect.
